itch, a monk by the name of Aamaleb came running in and right away started taking the spawn. Through curtesy, I asked him to leave, this was a camped spawn. His reply was &quot;You leave, I was here first&quot; .. &quot;PL elsewhere, I was here first&quot;...&quot;what is your problem, I was here first&quot;<br><br>Notice, he kept saying he was there first when he came upon US here. He then sat in the middle of the camp so he'd agro the orcs first. After asking him to leave repeatedly, I decided that if he was going to be rude, I'd not let him steal the camp spawn which Galadria and I had announced we were camping. I petitioned it, as did Galadria ... but no GM's were on I think ... <br><br>Anyways, it was a good way to ruin anyones day when someone so rude and selfish just waltz's in and decides you aren't suppose to be there and that it's now his camp. I do know a few ppl like this and I find that nothing pisses me off more. Needless to say, it went as you prolly guessed. Galadria and I easily killed the spawns and he finally gave up, his parting choice of words &quot;I'm tired of your childishness, I'm gonna go&quot; ... I laughed at him as he turned and ran off.<br><br>Aamaleb has shown his disregard for the rules of engagement and the rules of conduct. I would advise anyone who sees this guy to stay clear of him. A noted KS'er now, he isn't to be trusted. He even wanted to have me duel his high lvl whatever for rights to the spawn of the orc camp! ... *shakes his head in dismay*..<br><br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub44.ezboard.com/beverquestersofnorrath.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=tassius>Tassius</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 67<br> <font color=#8B4513>(5/31/01 1:17:53 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub44.ezboard.com/feverquestersofnorrathfrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=10.topic&index=1>Reply<