ut and you'll find youself at the very least being scratched!<br><br>This guy made the game for all around him a real bummer for a good 40 very long minutes... I don't understand how ANYONE can be so obstinately intent on ruining the fun for others. Had we been allowed to bring up Ordained's alt the way we intended, we would have occupied the camp for only another 10 or 15 minutes and been gone, which is in fact what happened when that child finally left.<br><br>Galadria<br>&quot;My joy is in Victus Fortis&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub44.ezboard.com/feverquestersofnorrathfrm19.showPrevMessage?topicID=10.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub44.ezboard.com/feverquestersofnorrathfrm19.showNextMessage?topicID=10.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub44.ezboard.com/feverquestersofnorrathfrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=10.topic&index=2><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/classic/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub44.ezboard.com/feverquestersofnorrathfrm19.emailToFriend?topicID=10.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub44.ezboard.com/feverquestersofnorrathfrm19.threadControl?topicID=10.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/classic/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub44.ezboard.com/feverquestersofnorrathfrm19.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=10.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub44.ezboard.com/feverquestersofnorrathfrm19.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=10.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification